{"id":18091,"date":"2022-12-31T04:31:36","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:31:36","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-nam-2022.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:31:36","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:31:36","slug":"nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-nam-2022","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-nam-2022\/","title":{"rendered":"Nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe s\u1ebd ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2022"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u00f4 t\u00f4 ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n do doanh s\u1ed1 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m, chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i sang xe \u0111i\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">2022, m\u1ed9t n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7y bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng xe h\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.  VinFast l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n xe x\u0103ng t\u1eeb 15\/7 v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n sang xe \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2023 v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea1t doanh s\u1ed1 cao nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal subtitle\">VinFast Fadil, Lux A2.0, Lux SA2.0<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"VinFast Lux A2.0, m\u1ed9t trong ba m\u1eabu xe ch\u1ea1y x\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng xe Vi\u1ec7t ng\u1eebng kinh doanh t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7.  \u1ea2nh: L\u01b0\u01a1ng D\u0169ng\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao.jpg\" title=\"nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">VinFast Lux A2.0, m\u1ed9t trong ba m\u1eabu xe ch\u1ea1y x\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng xe Vi\u1ec7t ng\u1eebng kinh doanh t\u1eeb gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 7.  \u1ea2nh: L\u01b0\u01a1ng D\u0169ng<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1eebng h\u1eb3n xe m\u00e1y x\u0103ng, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u xe Vi\u1ec7t n\u00e2ng th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe l\u00ean 10 n\u0103m v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb g\u1ea5p r\u01b0\u1ee1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng linh ki\u1ec7n, ph\u1ee5 t\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa, thay th\u1ebf.  Ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5.  VinFast b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u giao m\u1eabu \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean VF e34 t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2021. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 4\/2022, nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfp theo trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd d\u1ea7n l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 VF 8, ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 VF 9. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e3ng xe Vi\u1ec7t h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 VF 5.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal subtitle\">Ford Ecosport<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"EcoSport ng\u1eebng kinh doanh t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 3\/2022. \u1ea2nh: FVN\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_973_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao.jpg\" title=\"1672423083_973_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_973_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_973_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_973_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">EcoSport ng\u1eebng kinh doanh t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 3\/2022. \u1ea2nh: FVN<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u00e3ng xe Vi\u1ec7t tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n xe \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong, Ford EcoSport l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u201ckhai t\u1eed\u201d k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 3.  EcoSport l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014 v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh gia v\u1ecb m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam.  .<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">EcoSport gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u cho nh\u00f3m xe \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb g\u1ea7m cao c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf.  H\u00e3ng xe M\u1ef9 cho bi\u1ebft EccSport s\u1ebd ng\u1eebng l\u1eafp r\u00e1p t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2022 v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eabu xe kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nhu c\u1ea7u th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.  Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 do t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n M\u1ef9 c\u01a1 c\u1ea5u l\u1ea1i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n cung \u1ee9ng linh ki\u1ec7n.  EcoSport l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal subtitle\">Huyndai Kona<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Hyundai Kona ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 6\/2022. \u1ea2nh: Hyundai\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_611_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao.jpg\" title=\"1672423083_611_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_611_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_611_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_611_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Hyundai Kona ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 6\/2022. \u1ea2nh: Hyundai<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Kona, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a EcoSport, \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1eebng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam do thi\u1ebfu linh ki\u1ec7n, Hyundai chia s\u1ebb.  H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 5, h\u00e3ng xe H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u1ea1m d\u1eebng kinh doanh Kona v\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m.  Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Hyundai t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o Creta, m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu SUV c\u1ee1 B kh\u00e1c.  Kona \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n ra t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2018, ngay t\u1eeb khi b\u00e1n ra xe lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal subtitle\">Toyota Rush, Wigo, Hilux<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Toyota Wigo ng\u1eebng kinh doanh t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 3.  \u1ea2nh: TOYOTA\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_480_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao.jpg\" title=\"1672423083_480_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_480_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_480_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_480_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Toyota Wigo ng\u1eebng kinh doanh t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 3.  \u1ea2nh: TOYOTA<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Toyota kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n Rush v\u00e0 Avanza c\u0169 khi c\u1eb7p Avanza Premio v\u00e0 Veloz Cross xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.  M\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n do doanh s\u1ed1 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Rush, m\u1eabu xe c\u1ee1 A Wigo ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi h\u1ebft h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 3.  H\u00e3ng xe Nh\u1eadt t\u1ea1m d\u1eebng nh\u1eadp th\u00eam \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi.  So v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Wigo ch\u01b0a thu h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch Vi\u1ec7t.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Hilux, m\u1eabu b\u00e1n t\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Toyota, c\u0169ng t\u1ea1m ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n do lo ng\u1ea1i ngu\u1ed3n cung m\u00e1y d\u1ea7u ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n Euro 5 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong th\u00e1ng 7.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal subtitle\">Honda Brio<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Honda Brio ng\u1eebng kinh doanh t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7.  \u1ea2nh: L\u01b0\u01a1ng D\u0169ng\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_85_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao.jpg\" title=\"1672423083_85_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_85_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_85_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672423083_85_nhung-mau-xe-se-ngung-ban-tai-viet-nam-vao.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Honda Brio ng\u1eebng kinh doanh t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7.  \u1ea2nh: L\u01b0\u01a1ng D\u0169ng<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Toyota Hilux, Honda Brio c\u0169ng b\u1ecb ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n do kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i Euro 5.  Nh\u1eefng xe b\u00e1n ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n Euro 4.  Honda kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i Brio.  M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, m\u1eabu hatchback c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf \u0111ang d\u1ea7n gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00ednh Indonesia khi\u1ebfn Honda kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t do ngu\u1ed3n cung khan hi\u1ebfm.  Doanh s\u1ed1 Brio lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n xe c\u1ee1 A.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Minh V\u0169<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u00f4 t\u00f4 ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n do doanh s\u1ed1 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m, chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i sang xe \u0111i\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i. 2022, m\u1ed9t n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7y bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng xe h\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. VinFast l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ng\u1eebng b\u00e1n [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":17493,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18091"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18091"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18091\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/17493"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=18091"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=18091"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=18091"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}